<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Text Property</title>
    <style> *{
        margin:0;
        padding:0;
    }
        
           #head{
            background-color: rgb(243, 149, 168);
             

             text-decoration:underline;
             text-decoration-color: chartreuse;
             text-transform: uppercase;

           }
           #link{
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: capitalize;
           }
           .article{
             line-height:30px; 
             font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 900; 
            font-style: italic;
            font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
           }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2> <div id="head"> THis is the second heading </div></h2> 
    <a id="link" href="#">THis is Link</a><br>
    <p class="article" >  Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Soluta provident saepe perspiciatis sunt fugit pariatur voluptatum, nobis amet, minima labore esse facere sint reiciendis blanditiis! Deserunt quae quo perferendis optio!</p>
    


    
</body>
</html>